reviewText: Very cool rare film which now has cult status.  Glad to have a copy of it!  Very quick speedy service, the item arrived in the mail in only a few days.
This is an awful movie but there are some diehard fans who may like it.  Amazon's "editorial review" butchers the spelling of the star's name.  It should be "Magda Konopka".
Awesome 1970's movie ! Out of approximately 3000  movies I've seen in my life I rank this about 145. 95 th percentile, it's that good.

You get a couple quick glimpses of topless nudity every once in a while.  Theres a good strip routine near the end, but its so dark that you don't see much when she finally takes off her top.  you get a few glimpses, you will find more skin flicks than this.
